UID:Lobw4J_HhcdT5SxcuJJrg
SUMMARY:Kraken Pregame in the Armory 25/26
DTSTAMP:20260323T153918Z
DTSTART:20260405T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:Pregame at the Armory\, presented by WaFd Bank\, is your go-to 
	spot for game day vibes before every Kraken weekend home game at Climate P
	ledge Arena. Two hours before puck drop\, the Armory comes alive with Krak
	en energy.\n\nhttps://www.seattlecenter.com/events/event-calendar/kraken-p
